<span id="freeTextContainer4405487880716239441">Ambition, corruption, emotion.<br/>The fear of looking weak. The fear of losing status. Inability to admit one is wrong and to change course. Inability to speak truth to power. Inability of power to act on truth when it is spoken to.<br/>So it is, was...and will be?<br/>There are some very sobering thoughts in here, and an urgent call to examine our own course of folly and, if possible, address the issue.</span>

