      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/279244-the-march-of-folly-from-troy-to-vietnam">Quotes from The March of Foll...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;No one is so sure of his premises as the man who knows too little.&rdquo;</span>
